# SMTP Configuration (env-only for this deployment)
# This repository is configured to read SMTP settings exclusively from
# environment variables (recommended for container / Docker deployments).
# The web UI will not persist SMTP settings to the database in this mode;
# to change SMTP credentials update your container/environment secrets and
# restart/redeploy the container.
# SMTP_SERVER=smtp.gmail.com
# SMTP_PORT=587
# SMTP_USERNAME=your-email@gmail.com
# SMTP_PASSWORD=your-app-password
# FROM_EMAIL=your-email@gmail.com